product_entries.section_context_for_this_product_block: GEOTECH > DESIGN & INSTALLATION OF STONE COLUMNS > STONE COLUMNS BY VIBROFLOAT METHOD
product_entries.full_product_description: Supply and filling of approved sand as per specifications in sand blankets over stone columns including cost of sand, royalties, transportation to site, spreading, watering, ramming and compaction in layers of 150 mm loose thickness to achieve 85% relative density as per IS:2720 Part XIV, including preparation of sub-grade, dressing to the required slopes with all leads and lifts, testing, etc. complete as per drawings, specifications and directions of Engineer-in Charge.
product_entries.feature_or_specifications: material: approved sand, royalty: included, transportation: included, spreading: included, watering: included, ramming: included, compaction: included, relative density: 85%, standard: IS:2720 Part XIV (indian standard 2720 Part XIV), sub-grade preparation: included, dressing: included, leads and lifts: all, testing: included, as per drawings, specifications and directions of Engineer-in-Charge
